and proposed a replacement name 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159672EF3FF97AB8F34" authorityName="Weise" authorityYear="1922" box="[1052,1242,1023,1046]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Platyxantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bella">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159672EF3FF97AB8F34" box="[1052,1242,1023,1046]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Platyxantha bella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for Jacobyʼs species. Subsequent authors (
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFE50159676FF41F97828F14" author="MAULIK S." bookContentInfo="xiv + 648 pp. + 1 pl." box="[1117,1267,1055,1078]" editor="SEWELL R. B. S." firstAuthor="MAULIK" journalOrPublisher="Taylor and Francis, London" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" refId="ref32093" refString="MAULIK S. 1936: Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae (Galerucinae). In: SEWELL R. B. S. (ed.): The fauna of British India including Ceylon and Burma. Taylor and Francis, London, xiv + 648 pp. + 1 pl." title="Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae (Galerucinae)" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="The fauna of British India including Ceylon and Burma" year="1936">MAULIK 1936</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFE501596633F41F96E48F14" author="WILCOX J. A." box="[1281,1429,1055,1078]" editor="WILCOX J. A." firstAuthor="WILCOX" journalOrPublisher="Editio seconda. W. Junk, ' s-Gravenhage" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" pagination="433 - 664" refId="ref33616" refString="WILCOX J. A. 1973: Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae: Luperini: Luperina. In: WILCOX J. A. (ed.): Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa. Pars 78 (3). Editio seconda. W. Junk, ' s-Gravenhage, pp. 433 - 664." title="Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae: Luperini: Luperina" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa. Pars 78 (3)." year="1973">WILCOX 1973</bibRefCitation>
) classified 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE501596096F43F972E8F74" authorityName="Weise" authorityYear="1922" box="[932,1119,1087,1110]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Platyxantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bella">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE501596096F43F972E8F74" box="[932,1119,1087,1110]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Platyxantha bella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159674CF43F97818F74" authorityName="Baly" authorityYear="1861" box="[1150,1264,1087,1110]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Palpoxena" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159674CF43F97818F74" box="[1150,1264,1087,1110]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Palpoxena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. I examined one male 
<typeStatus id="5B5CE1EAFFE501596047F45F90B98F54" box="[885,968,1119,1142]" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">syntype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE5015960DBF45F97E98F54" authorityName="Jacoby" authorityYear="1889" box="[1001,1176,1119,1142]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Dorydea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="basalis">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE5015960DBF45F97E98F54" box="[1001,1176,1119,1142]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Dorydea basalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
deposited in MSNG and photograph of additional 
<typeStatus id="5B5CE1EAFFE50159677DF47F97D38FB4" box="[1103,1186,1151,1174]" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">syntype</typeStatus>
in MCZ. Undoubtedly this species belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159671BF49F97EE8F94" authorityName="Thunberg" authorityYear="1814" box="[1065,1183,1183,1206]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Taumacera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159671BF49F97EE8F94" box="[1065,1183,1183,1206]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Taumacera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and is close to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE501596609F49F96E48F94" authorityName="Jacoby" authorityYear="1889" box="[1339,1429,1183,1206]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Dorydea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="indica">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE501596609F49F96E48F94" box="[1339,1429,1183,1206]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">T. indica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159600EF4BF97C68FF4" authority="Duvivier, 1884" authorityName="Duvivier" authorityYear="1884" box="[828,1207,1215,1238]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Platyxantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="basalis">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159600EF4BF97618FF4" box="[828,1040,1215,1238]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Platyxantha basalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFE501596724F4BF97C68FF4" author="DUVIVIER A." box="[1046,1207,1215,1238]" firstAuthor="Duvivier" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin ou Comptes-Rendus des Sceances de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" pagination="cccx-cccxx" part="1884" refId="ref30757" refString="DUVIVIER A. 1884: Description de quelques phytophages nouveaux et notes rectificatives. Bulletin ou Comptes-Rendus des Sceances de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 1884: cccx-cccxx." title="Description de quelques phytophages nouveaux et notes rectificatives" type="journal volume" year="1884">Duvivier, 1884</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is here transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159600EF4DF90AC8FD4" authorityName="Laboissiere" authorityYear="1933" box="[828,989,1247,1270]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hoplosaenidea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159600EF4DF90AC8FD4" box="[828,989,1247,1270]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Hoplosaenidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see below). However the name 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159660DF4DF976D8E34" authority="Jacoby, 1889" authorityName="Jacoby" authorityYear="1889" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Dorydea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="basalis">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159660DF4DF90F98E34" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Dorydea basalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFE5015960BDF4FF976D8E34" author="JACOBY M." box="[911,1052,1279,1302]" firstAuthor="Jacoby" journalOrPublisher="Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" pagination="147 - 237" part="27" refId="ref31279" refString="JACOBY M. 1889: Viaggio di Leonardo Fea in Birmania e regioni vicine. - List of the phytophagous Coleoptera obtained by Signor L. Fea at Burmah and Tenasserim, with descriptions of the new species. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova 27: 147 - 237." title="Viaggio di Leonardo Fea in Birmania e regioni vicine. - List of the phytophagous Coleoptera obtained by Signor L. Fea at Burmah and Tenasserim, with descriptions of the new species" type="journal article" year="1889">Jacoby, 1889</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
cannot be restored as a valid name because it is permanently invalid based on Art. 59.3 of the Code (
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFE501596098F53F975B8E74" author="ICZN" bookContentInfo="306 pp." box="[938,1066,1343,1366]" firstAuthor="ICZN" journalOrPublisher="International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" refId="ref31036" refString="ICZN 1999: International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London, 306 pp." title="International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition" type="book" year="1999">ICZN 1999</bibRefCitation>
). The valid name of this species is 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFE50159600EF55F970A8E54" authority="Weise, 1922" authorityName="Weise" authorityYear="1922" baseAuthorityName="Bezděk" baseAuthorityYear="2019" box="[828,1147,1375,1398]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Taumacera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bella" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFE50159600EF55F909F8E54" box="[828,1006,1375,1398]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="30">Taumacera bella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFE5015960C7F55F970A8E54" author="WEISE J." box="[1013,1147,1375,1398]" firstAuthor="Weise" journalOrPublisher="Tijdschrift voor Entomologie" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" pagination="39 - 130" part="65" refId="ref33557" refString="WEISE J. 1922: Chrysomeliden der Indo-Malayischen Region. Tijdschrift voor Entomologie 65: 39 - 130." title="Chrysomeliden der Indo-Malayischen Region" type="journal article" year="1922">Weise, 1922</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="ADA03E21FFE5015967B7F55F978D8E54" box="[1157,1276,1375,1398]" pageId="7" pageNumber="30" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
